accepted_answer:
Both of your struct definitions, appdata and v2f have a colon in place of a semi-colon for the float4 vertex.
The correct syntax would be:
struct appdata
{
    float4 vertex : POSITION;
    float2 uv : TEXCOORD0;
    float4 color : COLOR;
};

struct v2f
{
    float4 vertex : SV_POSITION;
    float2 uv : TEXCOORD0;
    float4 color : COLOR;
};

